content: I'm going to give it 5 stars for one because it's a cool game and I like the nostalgia factor, and two, because I can play with my bluetooth controller!! So impressed with that aspect of the game. Overall, it's a short game but worth buying IMO.
Good. Actually has controller support in game too, just doesn't work on the menus. Be worthy of five stars with full controller support, including menus.
There is a bit confusion on how the gameplay is when in water, sometimes it jumps high and sometimes it does a normal jump. Can this be explained?
Good game a mix old school platformers!

Short,but really good. I enjoyed the very Kirby like game. :3 üëç The downsides would be it's hard to get the whip to attach to the nodes and that it's only 5 stages long. Achievements and more levels would be a nice addition someday.
